#uncutgems #videoessay #adamsandler 

Uncut Gems might be one of the most intense films of the century—and in this video I break down the scene that makes it truly unforgettable. From its chaotic editing and restless camerawork to the way it pulls real-life figures like Kevin Garnett and The Weeknd into its story, the Safdie brothers craft a piece of cinema that feels alive and unpredictable.
title: When your movie is too much to watch
